Common String Methods

charAt()	Returns the character at the specified index (position)	--> Return : char

concat()	Appends a string to the end of another string -->	Return : String

contains()	Checks whether a string contains a sequence of characters -->	Return : boolean

endsWith()	Checks whether a string ends with the specified character(s) --> Return :	boolean

equals()	Compares two strings. Returns true if the strings are equal, and false if not -->	Return : boolean

equalsIgnoreCase()	Compares two strings, ignoring case considerations -->	Return : boolean

indexOf()	Returns the position of the first found occurrence of specified characters in a string	--> Return : int

isEmpty()	Checks whether a string is empty or not	  Return : boolean

lastIndexOf()	Returns the position of the last found occurrence of specified characters in a string --> Return :	int

length()	Returns the length of a specified string -->  Return :int

replace()	Searches a string for a specified value, and returns a new string where the specified values are replaced --> return : String

replaceFirst()	Replaces the first occurrence of a substring that matches the given regular expression with the given replacement	--> return : String

replaceAll()	Replaces each substring of this string that matches the given regular expression with the given replacement	--> Return : String

split()	Splits a string into an array of substrings	--> Return : String[]

startsWith()	Checks whether a string starts with specified characters --> Return :	boolean

substring()	Returns a new string which is the substring of a specified string	--> Return : String

toCharArray()	Converts this string to a new character array --> Return :	char[]

toLowerCase()	Converts a string to lower case letters  --> Return : String

toString()	Returns the value of a String object --> Return :	String

toUpperCase()	Converts a string to upper case letters	--> Return : String

trim()	Removes whitespace from both ends of a string --> Return :	String

valueOf()	Returns the string representation of the specified value	--> Return : String